Of the following expressions the one equal to $ \frac{a^{-1}b^{-1}}{a^{-3} - b^{-3}}$ is:\\
\\
$ \textbf{(A)}\ \frac{a^2b^2}{b^2 - a^2}\qquad 
\textbf{(B)}\ \frac{a^2b^2}{b^3 - a^3}\qquad 
\textbf{(C)}\ \frac{ab}{b^3 - a^3}\qquad 
\textbf{(D)}\ \frac{a^3 - b^3}{ab}\qquad 
\textbf{(E)}\ \frac{a^2b^2}{a - b}$
